00:01:30,549 --> 00:01:34,344
maintain a specialized unit
to deal with the seedy mayhem.

34
00:03:06,103 --> 00:03:10,982
Interesting. I gotcha. Okay.
But you've still gotta do it.

35
00:03:11,024 --> 00:03:13,193
Sorry. Nobody can get any info

36
00:03:13,235 --> 00:03:15,404
on the weapon used to
assassinate Khans.

37
00:03:15,445 --> 00:03:17,239
This gets weirder the
more that we dig.

38
00:03:17,280 --> 00:03:19,116
What do you mean?

39
