[KEI] They should at least
be able to figure out

40
00:03:20,826 --> 00:03:22,911
whether the gun was
smuggled in or stolen.

41
00:03:22,953 --> 00:03:24,413
They've checked all
the normal channels,

42
00:03:24,454 --> 00:03:26,707
but nothing turned up.
Just dead ends.

43
