[TILARNA] It's seems like a
common weapon. But, then...

44
00:03:36,216 --> 00:03:38,844
[KEI] That campaign slogan
seems awkwardly suggestive

45
00:03:38,885 --> 00:03:40,637
for a guy accused
of sex crimes,

46
00:03:40,679 --> 00:03:43,056
but it kinda makes me
wanna vote for him.

47
00:03:43,098 --> 00:03:44,141
[TILARNA]
It does?

48
00:03:44,182 --> 00:03:46,226
Can't you tell when
I'm joking yet?

49
00:03:47,686 --> 00:03:49,271
[KEI]
This is it.

50
00:03:53,066 --> 00:03:58,071
[REPORTERS chattering]

51
00:04:01,158 --> 00:04:01,867
Listen, Kei.

52
00:04:01,908 --> 00:04:04,745
If we do get a chance to
meet with Mozeleemay...

53
