Are you picking up any "dead guy
puppet" stink around here?

57
00:04:22,763 --> 00:04:25,056
[sniffs]
I don't think so.

58
00:04:25,098 --> 00:04:28,143
At least, I smell no latena,
if that's what you mean.

59
00:04:28,185 --> 00:04:29,019
Detective.

60
00:04:29,060 --> 00:04:32,814
[KEI] Hm? Oh, hello.
Wait, don't tell me, Randall?

61
00:04:32,856 --> 00:04:35,358
Yup. Kevin Randall.
Good memory you got there.

62
00:04:35,400 --> 00:04:36,318
It's been a minute.

63
00:04:36,359 --> 00:04:38,361
[KEI] This guy's a journalist
who interviewed me

64
00:04:38,403 --> 00:04:40,572
once upon a time.

65
00:04:40,614 --> 00:04:43,909
Can't really chat now, Kevin,
we're on the clock.

66
00:04:43,950 --> 00:04:45,660
[RANDALL] So they got
you on the case.

67
00:04:45,702 --> 00:04:48,663
Looking for the culprit in the
Kahns assassination, I mean.

68
00:04:48,705 --> 00:04:50,207
[KEI]
No comment.

69
00:04:50,248 --> 00:04:53,293
Hi, there! I'm guessing
you're Matoba's new partner.

70
00:04:53,335 --> 00:04:56,421
You look like a Semanian,
how interesting.

71
00:04:56,463 --> 00:04:57,422
My name is‐‐

72
00:04:57,464 --> 00:04:58,840
No comment.

73
00:05:01,718 --> 00:05:04,721
Hey, Detective. I'm gonna
shoot you an email.

74
00:05:04,763 --> 00:05:06,389
You and I should talk soon.

75
00:05:06,431 --> 00:05:08,517
[KEI]
Sure, sure, we'll do that.

76
00:05:08,558 --> 00:05:11,228
[RANDALL] I'm serious,
it's really important.

77
00:05:11,269 --> 00:05:13,313
You'll see in my message.

78
00:05:15,273 --> 00:05:16,274
[MOZELEEMAY]
So, I told him,

79
00:05:16,316 --> 00:05:18,109
"Fine, but you have
to vote for me!"

80
00:05:18,151 --> 00:05:20,403
‐‐[knocking]
‐‐Yes, who's there?

81
00:05:20,445 --> 00:05:23,240
[KEI] Detective Matoba.
San‐Teresa Police.

82
00:05:23,281 --> 00:05:24,574
Nice to see you again.

83
00:05:24,616 --> 00:05:28,578
[MOZELEEMAY]
Huh? Ahem. Uh, sorry, guys.

84
00:05:28,620 --> 00:05:30,539
Give us the room for a few
minutes, if you wouldn't mind.

85
00:05:30,580 --> 00:05:31,790
[MALE ATTENDANT A]
Sure.

86
00:05:34,251 --> 00:05:36,878
[MOZELEEMAY] You said you're
with the San‐Teresa police?

87
00:05:36,920 --> 00:05:40,131
[KEI] That's right. I'd like
to ask you a few questions

88
00:05:40,173 --> 00:05:42,634
about the mayoral race.

89
00:05:42,676 --> 00:05:44,719
I've nothing of note to
say on the subject.

90
00:05:44,761 --> 00:05:46,263
If you have specific questions,

91
00:05:46,304 --> 00:05:47,681
you're going to have
to email my staff.

92
00:05:47,722 --> 00:05:50,934
[MARLA] Darling, what's the
harm in talking with them?

93
00:05:50,976 --> 00:05:52,269
[MOZELEEMAY]
Marla.

94
00:05:54,646 --> 00:05:55,897
You have nothing to hide,

95
00:05:55,939 --> 00:05:58,108
so I see no reason why
you shouldn't cooperate.

96
00:05:58,149 --> 00:06:00,110
Avoiding them just
looks suspicious.

97
00:06:00,151 --> 00:06:02,904
You're a hero of the people.
A politician who stood up

98
00:06:02,946 --> 00:06:05,323
to help Semanians
living in poverty.

99
00:06:05,365 --> 00:06:08,243
Now then, Detective,
ask whatever you wish.

100
00:06:08,285 --> 00:06:10,328
Thank you, I appreciate that.

101
00:06:10,370 --> 00:06:12,998
I'd like to start with
Kahns' assassination.

102
00:06:13,039 --> 00:06:13,540
Look, that‐‐

103
00:06:13,582 --> 00:06:15,834
[MARLA]
Just awful, such a tragedy.

104
00:06:15,876 --> 00:06:16,793
Since it happened,

105
00:06:16,835 --> 00:06:19,421
we've increased security
measures substantially.

106
00:06:19,462 --> 00:06:22,215
We're triple‐screening
everyone who comes onsite.

107
00:06:22,257 --> 00:06:24,843
Good for you, but according
to the rumors.

108
00:06:24,885 --> 00:06:27,137
You're gonna get at least
200,000 more votes

109
00:06:27,178 --> 00:06:28,763
now that Kahns is
out of the race.

110
00:06:28,805 --> 00:06:30,849
Got any comment on that?

111
00:06:30,891 --> 00:06:33,059
That's true, but the new
polls suggest that Tourte

112
00:06:33,101 --> 00:06:35,312
stands to gain 300,000.

113
00:06:35,353 --> 00:06:37,939
My husband is in
danger of losing.

114
00:06:37,981 --> 00:06:39,566
We've actually been
brainstorming ways

115
00:06:39,608 --> 00:06:41,151
to turn things around.

116
00:06:41,192 --> 00:06:43,778
Well, if Tourte is the
next one to bite the dust,

117
00:06:43,820 --> 00:06:46,323
you won't have to worry
about it, will ya?

118
00:06:46,364 --> 00:06:49,826
Listen, we Mozeleemays
are civilized people.

119
00:06:49,868 --> 00:06:52,078
And if everyone resolved
differences of opinion

120
00:06:52,120 --> 00:06:55,165
with guns, then the world
would devolve into a war zone.

121
00:06:55,206 --> 00:06:57,417
If one possessed the power
to control the dead,

122
00:06:57,459 --> 00:06:59,419
then weapons wouldn't
even be necessary.

123
00:06:59,461 --> 00:07:00,962
[MOZELEEMAY]
Control the dead?

124
00:07:01,004 --> 00:07:01,838
[MARLA]
Oh, yes.

125
00:07:01,880 --> 00:07:04,716
I've heard there are mildey
out there like that.

126
00:07:04,758 --> 00:07:07,886
However, you are aware that
regular Semanians don't possess

127
00:07:07,928 --> 00:07:11,556
the ability to use it, right?
Bonah Exedilica.

128
00:07:13,266 --> 00:07:13,767
[TILARNA grunts]

129
00:07:13,808 --> 00:07:15,226
[MARLA] Now, I don't
mean to run you off,

130
00:07:15,268 --> 00:07:17,687
but I'm afraid we're out
of time. Right, Darling?

131
00:07:17,729 --> 00:07:19,481
[MOZELEEMAY]
Oh... Yes.

132
00:07:22,651 --> 00:07:23,777
[KEI]
What's your take?

133
00:07:23,818 --> 00:07:25,820
[TILARNA]
One thing is abundantly clear.

134
00:07:25,862 --> 00:07:28,615
Mozeleemay is no leader, and his
wife is running the show.

135
00:07:28,657 --> 00:07:29,658
[KEI]
You think?

136
00:07:29,699 --> 00:07:32,744
She's got that man by the balls
and isn't afraid to squeeze.

137
00:07:32,786 --> 00:07:33,536
If anything...

138
00:07:33,578 --> 00:07:34,871
[TILARNA]
You felt it, too?

139
00:07:34,913 --> 00:07:36,623
[KEI]
Yep. Marla Mozeleemay.

140
00:07:36,665 --> 00:07:38,708
Her shit stinks worse
than her perfume.

141
00:07:38,750 --> 00:07:41,169
So, then, Zoey was
a victim of...

142
00:07:41,211 --> 00:07:44,089
Calm down. What we
need now is more info.

143
00:07:44,130 --> 00:07:46,508
I think our next step
should be talking to Tourte.

144
00:07:46,549 --> 00:07:47,175
[gunshots]

145
00:07:47,217 --> 00:07:49,386
[CROWD yelling]

146
00:07:50,971 --> 00:07:53,682
Wait! We need to figure
out what's going on!

147
00:07:59,062 --> 00:08:01,147
[KEI] San‐Teresa police.
Help us out.

148
00:08:01,189 --> 00:08:03,900
[CREWMAN A gasps]
Police? Well, um...

149
00:08:03,942 --> 00:08:05,276
Who was just shot?

150
00:08:05,318 --> 00:08:07,946
This is all so insane.
It was Mr. Mozeleemay.

151
00:08:07,988 --> 00:08:10,532
The opener had finished, and he
was just taking the stage.

152
00:08:10,573 --> 00:08:11,992
[CREWMAN B]
Whoa, check this out.

153
00:08:26,798 --> 00:08:28,341
Can you follow the perp?

154
00:08:28,383 --> 00:08:30,301
[CREWMAN A] We're trying to,
but I don't know if there's

155
00:08:30,343 --> 00:08:33,471
a clear enough shot of him for
our AI to make a positive ID.

156
00:08:33,513 --> 00:08:35,974
Ugh. I used his height and
clothing to run a search,

157
00:08:36,016 --> 00:08:39,811
but that turned up 91 hits.
Wait, sorry, 92.

158
00:08:39,853 --> 00:08:40,937
[KEI]
Walking speed.

159
00:08:40,979 --> 00:08:42,063
[CREWMAN A]
Uh?

160
00:08:42,105 --> 00:08:44,482
Eliminate people walking
over six miles per hour

161
00:08:44,524 --> 00:08:46,651
or who pushed the
person in front of them.

162
00:08:46,693 --> 00:08:49,362
After the crime,
assassins rarely run away.

163
00:08:49,404 --> 00:08:51,656
They try to blend in
with the crowd instead.

164
00:08:51,698 --> 00:08:53,074
[TILARNA grunts]

165
00:08:53,116 --> 00:08:54,868
[CREWMAN A]
We've narrowed it down to 31.

166
00:08:54,909 --> 00:08:57,370
[KEI] Let's look at the number
of times they turn around.

167
00:08:57,412 --> 00:08:59,330
Remove anyone who does
it three times or more

168
00:08:59,372 --> 00:09:01,124
within ten seconds.

169
00:09:01,166 --> 00:09:02,042
[CREWMAN A]
Now it's 17.

170
00:09:02,083 --> 00:09:04,169
People breathe through their
mouths when their heart rates

171
00:09:04,210 --> 00:09:06,046
go up, so knock out
the mouth breathers.

172
00:09:06,087 --> 00:09:08,298
[CREWMAN A]
Uh. We're down to three.

173
00:09:08,339 --> 00:09:10,050
[KEI]
Let me see those close up.

174
00:09:15,388 --> 00:09:18,558
[KEI grunts]
Where was this guy?

175
00:09:18,600 --> 00:09:20,643
[CREWMAN A] In the first floor
lobby on the north side,

176
00:09:20,685 --> 00:09:23,021
but he may have made
it outside by this point.

177
00:09:23,063 --> 00:09:25,065
[TILARNA, KEI grunt]

178
00:09:25,106 --> 00:09:26,274
[TILARNA]
Where's the north side lobby?

179
00:09:26,316 --> 00:09:26,775
[KEI]
That way!

180
00:09:26,816 --> 00:09:29,402
[TILARNA speaks Farbani]

181
00:09:34,365 --> 00:09:35,909
[MALE COP A]
This area's dangerous!

182
00:09:35,950 --> 00:09:37,911
Follow police
instructions exactly!

183
00:09:37,952 --> 00:09:40,580
[KEI] Police coming through!
Get out of the way, now!

184
00:09:40,622 --> 00:09:42,874
[MALE COP B]
Remain calm! Do not panic!

185
00:09:42,916 --> 00:09:43,750
[KEI]
Hey!

186
00:09:43,792 --> 00:09:48,755
[TILARNA speaks Farbani]

187
00:09:53,927 --> 00:09:55,553
[gasps]

188
00:09:59,224 --> 00:10:01,017
There he is! Kei!

189
00:10:01,059 --> 00:10:04,270
[KEI gasps] You, there,
in the black suit, freeze!

190
00:10:04,312 --> 00:10:06,606
Put your hands above
your head, nice and easy.

191
00:10:06,648 --> 00:10:07,774
[TILARNA]
Shoot him, now!

192
00:10:07,816 --> 00:10:09,109
[KEI grunts]

193
