[CROWD gasps, chatters]

194
00:10:10,026 --> 00:10:10,985
[KEI]
Shit!

195
00:10:11,528 --> 00:10:12,987
<i>Kizenya!</i>

196
00:10:13,196 --> 00:10:14,614
[MAN A gasps]

197
00:10:19,786 --> 00:10:20,829
Dammit!

198
00:10:20,870 --> 00:10:23,540
[CROWD gasps]

199
00:10:23,581 --> 00:10:24,666
[KEI grunts]

200
00:10:26,459 --> 00:10:28,044
[TILARNA]
Let's follow him!

201
00:10:37,887 --> 00:10:39,681
What the hell, something's off.

202
00:10:46,271 --> 00:10:47,564
[DRIVER A]
Oh?

203
00:10:47,605 --> 00:10:48,982
[KEI]
I need to borrow your car!

204
00:10:49,023 --> 00:10:50,108
I've no cash!

205
00:10:50,150 --> 00:10:53,111
What? No, your car! I'm a cop.

206
00:10:53,153 --> 00:10:55,196
Please be careful with her!

207
00:10:58,366 --> 00:11:00,368
[KEI]
Thanks for your cooperation!

208
00:11:06,666 --> 00:11:08,918
[KEI]
Tilarna Exedilica's location.

209
00:11:13,673 --> 00:11:15,091
[DRIVER B gasps]

210
00:11:19,679 --> 00:11:21,848
[KEI]
V‐twenty‐one to headquarters!

211
00:11:21,890 --> 00:11:25,018
I'm in pursuit of the suspect
who shot Coal Mozeleemay,

212
00:11:25,059 --> 00:11:28,605
approaching the vicinity
of New Compton!

213
00:11:28,646 --> 00:11:32,108
Suspect is a Semanian male,
approximately five foot nine,

214
00:11:32,150 --> 00:11:35,445
in a black suit.
He's armed and dangerous.

215
00:11:35,486 --> 00:11:36,571
[FEMALE OPERATOR A]
Roger that.

216
00:11:36,613 --> 00:11:38,531
Dispatching backup
to you right away.

217
00:11:38,573 --> 00:11:39,991
[KEI]
Hurry, please!

218
00:11:51,127 --> 00:11:53,671
[gasps]
Gotcha!

219
00:12:01,304 --> 00:12:02,680
[KEI gasps]

220
00:12:02,722 --> 00:12:05,600
[TILARNA grunting]

221
00:12:07,977 --> 00:12:08,978
[ASSASSIN grunts]

222
00:12:09,020 --> 00:12:10,230
[shouts]

223
00:12:10,271 --> 00:12:12,357
[ASSASSIN shouts]

224
00:12:12,398 --> 00:12:14,108
[KEI grunts]

225
00:12:16,319 --> 00:12:17,528
[KEI]
Don't move!

226
00:12:21,950 --> 00:12:25,745
‐‐[gunshots]
‐‐[ASSASSIN groans]

227
00:12:27,538 --> 00:12:30,041
[shouts]

228
00:12:35,129 --> 00:12:36,756
[ASSASSIN grunts]

229
00:12:37,507 --> 00:12:40,510
[KEI groans]

230
00:12:47,850 --> 00:12:51,646
‐‐[slicing]
‐‐[ASSASSIN groans]

231
00:12:54,023 --> 00:12:56,776
[TILARNA] Curses of Bedayah,
be visited upon your soul!

232
00:12:56,818 --> 00:12:58,152
[KEI]
Don't do it!

233
00:13:01,406 --> 00:13:02,907
Why did you stop me?

234
00:13:02,949 --> 00:13:05,743
[KEI] 'Cause you were about
to murder him. Chill out.

235
00:13:05,785 --> 00:13:08,371
What, the suspect's
fundamental rights again?

236
00:13:08,413 --> 00:13:10,790
[KEI] I'm trying to help
you be a good person,

237
00:13:10,832 --> 00:13:13,209
even if it feels
terrible in the moment.

238
